Bitpay,is,an,online,payment,service,that,uses,bitcoins,it,provides,people,a,platform,to,make,payments,online,The,BitPay,API,is,REST,based,which,enables,developers,to,integrate,its,services,into,their,applications,With,the,API,clients,can,create,and,manage,invoices,issue,refunds,manage,bills,and,more,Developers,may,call,the,API,directly,over,HTTP